# NETWORK::SET_LAST_VIEWED_SHOP_ITEM

## Parameters
* **INT** itemHash
* **INT** itemPrice
* **INT** shopNameHash

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Sets the id of the last visited store. Used to track the purchase flow
